other_services_use: commutation to day program if ride is guaranteed to be under 30 minutes long and arrive within 30 minute target window. Due to incontinence, longer rides are not possible without an aide present. Due to program requirements, earliness and lateness are not permitted.
other_rte_opt: Due to incontinence, longer rides will not work. Due to day program requirements, lateness or earliness are not allowed for arrival or departure.
